leocodebox
==========

leocodebox is a local-only desktop adaptation for controlling local coding agents.

This distribution is based on CloudCLI UI:
CloudCLI UI (https://github.com/siteboon/claudecodeui)

CloudCLI UI is licensed under AGPL-3.0-or-later with additional Section 7
attribution terms. See LICENSE for the full license text and required notices.

Modifications in this distribution include local-only desktop startup, removal of
hosted account flows from the product UI, leocodebox branding, and
desktop-managed local authentication for the bundled local service.

Provider switch functionality references CC Switch:
CC Switch (https://github.com/farion1231/cc-switch)

